data.meta_description: Dorival Caymmi is considered to be one of the most important songwriters in Brazilian popular music. The son of an Italian immigrant and a black Bahian woman, he had a distinctive style of his own and was the writer of many classic songs. The Sambas, such as O Samba Da Minha Terra, have become standards of Música...
